    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "return [{\n  json: {\n    intake_id: $json.intake_id,\n    patient_name: $json.patient_name,\n    raw_note: $json.raw_note,\n    doctor_advice: $json.doctor_advice || '',\n    geminiBody: {\n      contents: [\n        {\n          parts: [\n            {\n              text: `Ban la tro ly y khoa hau kham.\n\nYEU CAU BAT BUOC:\n1) Chi trich xuat thong tin da co trong du lieu bac si nhap.\n2) KHONG duoc suy dien, KHONG duoc tu bo sung gio uong thuoc, lieu dung hoac loi dan.\n3) Neu khong co thong tin thi de trong hoac ghi \"chua duoc chi dinh\".\n4) Truong doctorAdvice phai giu nguyen y nghia loi dan cua bac si.\n\nTra ve DUY NHAT JSON hop le (khong markdown, khong giai thich):\n\n{\n  \"diagnosis\": \"...\",\n  \"diagnosisSimplified\": \"...\",\n  \"doctorAdvice\": \"...\",\n  \"medications\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"...\",\n      \"dosage\": \"...\",\n      \"frequency\": \"...\",\n      \"timing\": \"...\",\n      \"days\": 0,\n      \"purpose\": \"...\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"instructions\": [\n    {\"action\":\"...\",\"timing\":\"...\",\"importance\":\"High|Medium|Low\"}\n  ],\n  \"redFlags\": [\n    {\"symptom\":\"...\",\"action\":\"...\"}\n  ],\n  \"followUp\": {\"date\":\"...\",\"action\":\"...\"},\\n  \"unaskedQuestions\": [\"...\"]\\n}\n\nGhi chu kham (raw_note):\n${$json.raw_note}\n\nLoi dan bac si (doctor_advice):\n${$json.doctor_advice || ''}`\n            }\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      generationConfig: { temperature: 0.1 }\n    }\n  }\n}];"
      },
      "id": "9ba9d506-9a4b-4636-9346-69bc058f9142",
      "name": "Build Gemini Request",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
